<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比、彼得和菲利斯在隧道里慢慢地走着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在找那个红衣服的男孩儿。他没有和其他孩子一起跑出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果火车来了，就紧紧靠着墙站好。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的声音在隧道里听上去很奇怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想回去。我不喜欢这里。”菲利斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不管你说什么，我都不想在黑乎乎的隧道里走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，菲利斯。”彼得说，“我有半根蜡烛和一些火柴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他停下来听了一会儿。“什么声音？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁轨上传来嗡嗡的声音，而且越来越大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是火车。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让我回去。”菲利斯大喊。她想挣脱鲍比抓着她的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别害怕。这里很安全。”鲍比说，“往这边站。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快过来！这里有个洞！”彼得大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在火车的声音已经非常大了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比拉着菲利斯，朝着彼得发出声音的方向走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>隧道的墙上有一个挖出来的洞，他们躲了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车的声音越来越大。他们觉得耳朵快要聋了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114141</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看到远远的车灯，就像龙的眼睛一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车好像在对着他们咆哮。菲利斯和鲍比紧紧抱在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车经过的时候，灯光非常刺眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们感到了一阵阵热气，还闻到了一股烟味儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得也害怕得紧紧抓着鲍比的胳膊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然他解释说那是因为“觉得她会害怕”才抓的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>慢慢地，声音变小了，灯光也越变越弱。呜！火车开出了隧道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”孩子们同时说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得用颤抖的手点亮了蜡烛。“快走吧。”他的声音也在颤抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”菲利斯说，“如果穿红衣服的男孩儿在火车轨道上怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须快点儿找到他。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走向隧道深处。彼得走在前面，拿着蜡烛照路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，彼得停下大喊：“有人吗？”然后他走得更快了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女孩儿们追上他，看到了那个男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得停在离他一米远的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯看到了红色的东西，于是她害怕得紧紧闭上眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>穿着红衣服的男孩儿躺在铁轨附近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他闭着眼睛，一动不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他……死了吗？”菲利斯闭着眼睛问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然没有！”彼得说，“他只是晕倒了。我们该怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们能搬得动他吗？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240480</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道，他个头挺大的。”彼得回答，“在他额头洒点儿水怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们没有水，但是有午餐时剩的牛奶。”鲍比说，“试试吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。我记得好像按摩手就可以让昏迷的人醒过来。”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是鲍比在他的额头上洒了些温牛奶，彼得按摩他的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，三个孩子一起说：“快醒醒！ 快醒醒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>